@startuml
title Authentication Flows

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam participantPadding 15
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

participant "Client" as Client

box "Colocated" #f9f9f0
  participant "LLM Gateway" as Gateway #fde8e8
  participant "Stargate" as SG #f0f7e8
end box

participant "NVCF API" as NVCF #f5e6ff
participant "Worker" as Worker #e8f4fd

== 1. Worker Registration (gRPC) ==
Worker -> SG: RegisterInferenceServer(stream open)\nAuthorization: Bearer <worker_identity_token>
SG -> NVCF: AuthLlmWorker(worker_identity_token)
NVCF --> SG: routing_key
SG -> SG: store routing_key with\nregistered worker identity

== 2. Worker QUIC Reverse Tunnel ==
Worker -> SG: QUIC connect + handshake\n(includes worker_identity_token)
SG -> NVCF: AuthLlmWorker(worker_identity_token)
NVCF --> SG: routing_key
SG -> SG: compare routing_key\nwith gRPC registration
SG --> Worker: ACK

== 3. Inference Request ==
Client -> Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions\nAuthorization: Bearer <api_key>\nnvcf-function-id: <function_id>\n\n{"model": "my-model", ...}
note right of Client
  nvcf-function-id header name
  is configurable.
end note
Gateway -> NVCF: validate api_key
NVCF --> Gateway: routing_key, allowed_models, rate_limits
note right of Gateway
  Response is cached.
end note

Gateway -> SG: POST /v1/chat/completions\nx-routing-key: <routing_key>\nx-model: <model>\nx-request-id: <request_id>\nx-input-tokens: <estimate>\n\n{"stream": true, ...}
SG -> SG: lookup registered workers\nmatching (routing_key, model)
SG -> Worker: proxied request over QUIC

@enduml
